<A>__{as sam drives the wagon, the other slaves trudge along side by foot. we should get the sense the travel is long and tedious.}
<L>__{exterior ford's work area later}
<A>__{it is a sizable work area on the edge of indian creek. there is much work being done, the slaves primarily employed in piling the timber and chopping it into lumber. as before, there is little doubt about the rigors of the job at hand. working as a carpenter at the work area is john tibeats. there are also various customers who move about placing orders.}
